  "text": "A dynamic scoping strategy is adopted for the eval operation, described by rule [CITATION_1] . In this case the localities of the spawned process are not interpreted by using the local allocation environment. Instead, the process is transmitted and its execution can be in uenced by the remote allocation environment.",
